sequenceDiagram
    actor U as User / Persona
    participant UI as EPMS UI / Teams
    participant BFF as BFF / API Layer
    participant AIO as AI Orchestrator
    participant PR as Persona Resolver
    participant AG as Persona Agent Runtime
    participant RAG as RAG / Knowledge Base
    participant LLM as LLM / Bedrock Model
    participant TOOL as Tool Layer / EPMS APIs
    participant JO as Journey Orchestrator
    participant AP as Human Approver
    participant AUD as Audit / Monitoring

    U->>UI: Ask complex <br/>question / <br/>request action
    UI->>BFF: Send AI request
    BFF->>AIO: Forward <br/>request with user context
    AIO->>PR: Resolve <br/>persona, policy, tools
    PR-->>AIO: Persona agent definition

    AIO->>AG: Initialize agent runtime
    AG->>RAG: Retrieve <br/>enterprise/project context
    RAG-->>AG: Relevant <br/>knowledge/context

    AG->>LLM: Plan steps/<br/>reason on task
    LLM-->>AG: Plan + required tool calls

    AG->>TOOL: Invoke EPMS<br/>APIs / external tools
    TOOL-->>AG: Return live business data

    AG->>LLM: Re-evaluate <br/>with tool results
    LLM-->>AG: Analysis + <br/>recommendations + <br/>proposed action

    alt Read-only or recommendation only
        AG-->>AIO: Final response
    else Non-critical execution
        AG->>TOOL: Execute permitted action
        TOOL-->>AG: Execution result
        AG-->>AIO: Final response <br/>with action status
    else Critical execution
        AG-->>AIO: Draft action <br/>requiring approval
        AIO->>JO: Start approval workflow
        JO->>AP: Request approval
        AP-->>JO: Approve / Reject
        alt Approved
            JO->>TOOL: Execute <br/>approved action
            TOOL-->>JO: Execution result
            JO-->>AIO: Approved and completed
        else Rejected
            JO-->>AIO: Rejected <br/>/ returned for review
        end
    end

    AIO->>AUD: Log prompt, <br/>tools, decisions, actions
    AIO-->>BFF: Return final outcome
    BFF-->>UI: Response
    UI-->>U: Show result